OL,3,CTommy Fleetwood reflects on
OL,4,C'emotional' Royal Birkdale
OL,6,FTommy Fleetwood vowed to keep chasing
OL,7,Fhis Open dream after a week he
OL,8,Fdescribed as "the most special ever"
OL,9,Fended in disappointment at Royal
OL,10,FBirkdale.
OL,12,FThe Southport native fell just short
OL,13,Fin his bid for glory at his hometown
OL,14,Fcourse on Sunday 19th July, finishing
OL,15,Fin a tie for fourth three shots behind
OL,16,Fwinner Ryan Fox on seven under.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@dO]
