OL,3,CTommy Fleetwood reflects on
OL,4,C'emotional' Royal Birkdale
OL,6,FFleetwood, starting five shots back,
OL,7,Felectrified the crowd when he holed
OL,8,Ffrom 73 feet for birdie at the first
OL,9,Fhole and picked up more shots on the
OL,10,Ffifth and eighth but could not
OL,11,Fmaintain the momentum.
OL,13,FThree successive bogeys around the
OL,14,Fturn proved costly but he did finish
OL,15,Fstrongly with birdies on the last two
OL,16,Fholes, much to the delight of the
OL,17,Fpartisan galleries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
