CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784556365
OL,3,CTommy Fleetwood reflects on
OL,4,C'emotional' Royal Birkdale
OL,6,FFleetwood said: "There's
OL,7,Fdisappointment that I didn't win today
OL,8,For I couldn't get it done when I was
OL,9,Fin a really good position ` but of
OL,10,Fcourse there's only one person that
OL,11,Fgets to win it, and my dream of
OL,12,Fwinning the Open will carry on and
OL,13,FI'll continue to chase it.
OL,15,F"But stuff like that, walking down 18
OL,16,Fand the atmosphere out there, that was
OL,17,Fbeyond stuff that I've dreamt of. That
OL,18,Fwas just stuff that I never imagined.
OL,26,@nD@QOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
