OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784556365
OL,3,CTommy Fleetwood reflects on
OL,4,C'emotional' Royal Birkdale
OL,6,F"The crowds were amazing, and they
OL,7,Fmade it the most special week ever for
OL,8,Fme, and I can't thank them enough."
OL,10,FFleetwood, 35, is still chasing his
OL,11,Ffirst major title and the realisation
OL,12,Fhe would miss out this time hit him
OL,13,Fwhen he failed to take advantage of
OL,14,Fthe par-five 14th.
OL,16,FHe said: "I felt that was a bit of a
OL,17,Fnail in the coffin, because I still
OL,18,Ffelt like I had a chance and I could
OL,19,Fhave a good finish.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]xD@JOU
