OL,3,CTommy Fleetwood reflects on
OL,4,C'emotional' Royal Birkdale
OL,6,F"On 14, I'm there, I'm greenside with
OL,7,Fa great chance, so that hurt a lot."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@dO]
